MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: This mapping is used to load the table BIWIP_MFG_SELL_XRF.
MAPPING.NAME: m_BIWIP_MFG_SELL_XRF

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Source qualifier to get required fields from BILL_OF_MTRLS.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_BILL_OF_MTRLS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MAX(BILL_OF_MTRLS.PARENT_STYLE) AS PARENT_STYLE, MAX(BILL_OF_MTRLS.PARENT_COLOR) AS PARENT_COLOR, MAX(BILL_OF_MTRLS.PARENT_ATTRIBUTE) AS PARENT_ATTRIBUTE, MAX(BILL_OF_MTRLS.PARENT_SIZE) AS PARENT_SIZE, BILL_OF_MTRLS.COMP_STYLE_CD, BILL_OF_MTRLS.COMP_COLOR_CD, BILL_OF_MTRLS.COMP_ATTRIBUTE_CD, BILL_OF_MTRLS.COMP_SIZE_CD FROM BILL_OF_MTRLS GROUP BY COMP_STYLE_CD, COMP_COLOR_CD, COMP_ATTRIBUTE_CD, COMP_SIZE_CD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Joiner Transformation for the tables STYLE and STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: JNR_STYLE_OCPO

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on SKU to get PACK_CD.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_STYLE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT B.STYLE_CD as STYLE_CD, B.PACK_CD as PACK_CD FROM STYLE B,CORP_DIVISION C Where B.CORP_DIVISION_CD=C.CORP_DIVISION_CD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Router Transformation is used to filter the records based on the groups ORIGIN_TYPE_CD = 'M' and ORIGIN_TYPE_CD IN('S','Z').
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: RTR_MFG_SELL

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Source qualifier to get required fields from MFG_SELLING_SKU_XREF.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_MFG_SELLING_SKU_XREF

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Expression Transfromation to pass additional values to the columns SELL_X_SIZE_CD,SELL_PACK_CD,CREATE_USERID and CREATE_TIMESTAMP.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_TO_PASS_VALUES

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Master Joiner with BU_SKU_XREF to get the corresponding Champion(chp) details.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: JNR_BU_SKU_XREF

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Join Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: chp_BU_STYLE = stg_STYLE_CD AND chp_BU_COLOR = stg_COLOR_CD_A AND chp_BU_SIZE_CD = stg_SIZE_CD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on SKU to get X_SIZE_CD
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SKU

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SKU.X_SIZE_CD as X_SIZE_CD, SKU.STYLE_CD as STYLE_CD, SKU.COLOR_CD as COLOR_CD, SKU.ATTRIBUTE_CD as ATTRIBUTE_CD, SKU.SIZE_CD as SIZE_CD FROM SKU

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_CD = I_STYLE_CD AND COLOR_CD = I_COLOR_CD AND ATTRIBUTE_CD = I_ATTRIBUTE_CD AND SIZE_CD = I_SIZE_CD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Expression Pass Through.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_PASS_THROUGH

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Expression is used to get the data for the additional columns SELL_STYLE_CD,SELL_COLOR_CD,SELL_SIZE_CD andSELL_ATTRIBUTE_CD.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_TO_GET_ADDITIONAL_DATA2

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Source qualifier to get required fields from STYLE.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_STYLE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT B.STYLE_CD, B.PACK_CD, B.ORIGIN_TYPE_CD, C.CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT FROM STYLE B , CORP_DIVISION C Where B.CORP_DIVISION_CD=C.CORP_DIVISION_CD AND B.ORIGIN_TYPE_CD IN ('M','S','Z')

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Aggregator to get distinct records.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: AGG_DISTINCT

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Master Joiner with MFG_SELLING_SKU_XREF to get the corresponding Manufacturing data details.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: JNR_MFG_SELLING_SKU_XREF

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Join Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: mfg_MFG_STYLE_CD = stg_STYLE_CD AND mfg_MFG_COLOR_CD = stg_COLOR_CD AND mfg_MFG_ATTRIBUTE_CD = stg_ATTRIBUTE_CD AND mfg_MFG_SIZE_CD = stg_SIZE_CD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Source qualifier to get required fields from stg_ow_corp_prod_order
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_STG_OW_CORP_PROD_ORDER

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select A.STYLE_CD, A.COLOR_CD, A.SIZE_CD, A.ATTRIBUTE_CD, A.AS_OF_DATE from stg_ow_corp_prod_order A where A.AS_OF_DATE= (select as_of_date from day_dimension where day_date = trunc(sysdate - 1)) and A.ORDER_STATUS_CD = 1 and A.STYLE_MATL_TYPE_CD in ( '00','01','02') and A.CORP_BUSINESS_UNIT in ( 'CHP','PRT','CSW','UNW')

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Union transformation to collect the data from both flows.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: UN_MFG_SELL

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Expression is used to get the data for the additional columns SELL_STYLE,SELL_COLOR,SELL_SIZE,SELL_ATTRIBUTE,SELL_BUSINESS_UNIT and ORG_PACK_CD.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_TO_GET_ADDITIONAL_DATA

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Source qualifier to get required fields from BU_SKU_XREF.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_BU_SKU_XREF

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Master Joiner with BILL_OF_MTRLS to get the corresponding assorted to component data details.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: JNR_BILL_OF_MTRLS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Join Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: bom_COMP_STYLE_CD = stg_STYLE_CD AND bom_COMP_COLOR_CD = stg_COLOR_CD AND bom_COMP_ATTRIBUTE_CD = stg_ATTRIBUTE_CD AND bom_COMP_SIZE_CD = stg_SIZE_CD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Master Joiner with IRREG_SKU_XREF to get the corresponding Irregular data details.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: JNR_IRREG_SKU_XREF

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Join Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: irr_STYLE_CD = stg_STYLE_CD AND irr_COLOR_CD = stg_COLOR_CD AND irr_SIZE_CD = stg_SIZE_CD AND irr_ATTRIBUTE_CD = stg_ATTRIBUTE_CD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Source qualifier to get required fields from IRREG_SKU_XREF.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_IRREG_SKU_XREF

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select IRREG_SKU_XREF.STYLE_CD, IRREG_SKU_XREF.COLOR_CD, IRREG_SKU_XREF.ATTRIBUTE_CD, IRREG_SKU_XREF.SIZE_CD, IRREG_SKU_XREF.IRREG_STYLE_CD, IRREG_SKU_XREF.IRREG_COLOR_CD, IRREG_SKU_XREF.IRREG_ATTRIBUTE_CD, IRREG_SKU_XREF.IRREG_SIZE_CD FROM da.irreg_SKU_XREF
